Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.69,0:01:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森里…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.50,0:01:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.21,0:01:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森里…先生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.51,0:01:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.65,0:01:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂马？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.97,0:02:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…萤之助？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.90,0:02:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.39,0:02:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与蓓儿丹蒂相遇之后
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.36,0:02:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有时会思考这个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.04,0:02:24.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天的梦也是某种预兆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.96,0:02:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.06,0:02:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.71,0:02:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.78,0:02:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 萤一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.70,0:02:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 蓓儿丹蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.52,0:02:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.17,0:02:49.07,Chapter,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H8EB1B7&}{\1c&H004993&}啊啊 各自的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.85,0:02:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前阵子在整理东西的时候发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.12,0:02:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是爷爷的日记
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.15,0:03:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爷爷叫“萤之助”啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.62,0:03:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比萤一你帅多了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.82,0:03:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要你管
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.59,0:03:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照片上的女人是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.97,0:03:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照片泛黄了 看不清了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.18,0:03:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真知子奶奶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.13,0:03:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地图？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.08,0:03:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像写了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.32,0:03:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“我一生的光辉就藏于此处”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.09,0:03:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.96,0:03:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.90,0:03:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 萤一 准备就绪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.88,0:03:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.04,0:03:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这种标记的地图当然就是藏宝图了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.14,0:03:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美妙的冒险在等待我们前去！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.90,0:03:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩电视看多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.58,0:03:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且马上就是机车社的合宿了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.59,0:03:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没那闲工夫和闲钱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.71,0:03:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没劲～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.43,0:03:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你们这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.38,0:03:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森里～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.75,0:03:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.05,0:04:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 猫实工大机车社体能训练合宿 开始～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.59,0:04:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么千寻前辈也来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.45,0:04:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还用问吗 因为觉得很有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.56,0:04:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.94,0:04:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对出合宿费的赞助商有什么怨言吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.99,0:04:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.14,0:04:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.92,0:04:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 这洋房真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.46,0:04:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房主似乎是爷爷的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.72,0:04:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打电话给他 他说可以便宜点租给我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.28,0:04:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉到了吧 蓓儿丹蒂？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.76,0:04:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 姐姐 有气息
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.85,0:04:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么东西…在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.94,0:04:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了 我是森里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.31,0:04:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.60,0:04:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是魔属的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.18,0:05:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就送你上西天！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.65,0:05:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久候大驾 欢迎来到本田庄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.70,0:05:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是代理负责人本田智惠子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.43,0:05:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.05,0:05:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请…请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.22,0:05:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.67,0:05:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森里先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.68,0:05:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还记得我们的约定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.83,0:05:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.29,0:05:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.05,0:05:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.01,0:05:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.84,0:05:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森里 没想到你还有两下子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.38,0:05:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已…已经有了姐姐还…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.75,0:05:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太肮脏了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.06,0:05:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 这一定是什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.04,0:06:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…你真的不记得我们的约定了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.20,0:06:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说约定了 我根本就不认识你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.92,0:06:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连我都不记得了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.19,0:06:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.51,0:06:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.00,0:06:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.11,0:06:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问 你们两位是什么关系？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.58,0:06:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这怎么说呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.09,0:06:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 我是很久以前就和森里先生约定好的！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.22,0:06:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.37,0:06:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.61,0:06:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上要开会了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.16,0:06:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在争风吃醋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.45,0:06:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么叫争风吃醋啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.10,0:06:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天也快黑了 今天就…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.82,0:06:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我来准备晚饭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.24,0:07:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.64,0:07:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.88,0:07:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女孩是思念体啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.07,0:07:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我知道 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.30,0:07:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.23,0:07:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些事情比较在意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.22,0:07:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.15,0:07:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思念体是什么意思啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.28,0:07:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某人留下强烈的情感而离开这个世界的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.80,0:07:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的情感就会聚合成实体
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.43,0:07:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是思念体
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.81,0:07:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽…幽灵？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.53,0:07:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.00,0:07:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要回家了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.63,0:07:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来将召开机车社合宿会议！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.14,0:07:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.99,0:07:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,36号大泷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.11,0:07:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始演唱！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.11,0:08:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.63,0:08:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被灌了不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.99,0:08:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.08,0:08:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何也想不起来…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.21,0:08:50.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的和你有过什么约定吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.10,0:08:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？为什么你会有那张照片？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.97,0:09:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.16,0:09:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的错觉吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.43,0:09:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓儿 你在听吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.05,0:09:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.83,0:09:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是 我决定开自己的店 自力更生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.29,0:09:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.67,0:09:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓儿也尝尝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.74,0:09:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.15,0:09:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个红薯的调味是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.88,0:09:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 森里 你去哪儿啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.69,0:09:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又想和蓓儿丹蒂前辈幽会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.49,0:09:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你喝多了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.18,0:09:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐刚才不是和大家在一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.38,0:10:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.05,0:10:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诗寇蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.89,0:10:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.33,0:10:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一和那个思念体都不在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.10,0:10:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.95,0:10:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.25,0:10:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.42,0:10:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真该盯着她的 她想附身萤一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.58,0:10:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.44,0:10:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.92,0:10:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思念体为了达到目的会不择手段的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.85,0:10:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诗寇蒂 长谷川
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.23,0:10:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这个房间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.84,0:10:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是晕了过去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.71,0:10:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开锁术不管用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.89,0:10:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 快开门！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.78,0:11:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你在里面 出来投降吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.95,0:11:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的 门是打不开的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.72,0:11:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 快点想起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.71,0:11:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天 你和我的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.29,0:11:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请履行诺言吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.55,0:11:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 鬼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.51,0:11:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是鬼吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.69,0:11:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 思念体不是妖魔 退魔程序是不管用的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.76,0:11:43.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 实现我的愿望 否则我决不会放开你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.25,0:11:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 你真的不知道他是谁吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.13,0:11:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.37,0:12:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是萤一 不是你所等的萤之助！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.61,0:12:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事…已经无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.24,0:12:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和萤之助先生相遇在夏天 仅仅只相处了4天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.75,0:12:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他与因病来疗养的我许下约定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.60,0:12:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我被病魔纠缠之时 那是我精神的支柱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.04,0:12:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我已经离开人世
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.83,0:12:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但依然一直等待着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.43,0:12:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而他终于来见我了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.26,0:12:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是世代更迭 也有着命运的指引…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.31,0:12:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请告诉我 你和萤之助先生做了怎样的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.13,0:13:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？我怎么会睡着了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.58,0:13:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 萤一
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.60,0:13:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带你去看样东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.98,0:13:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在地下室有什么让我看的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.06,0:13:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.52,0:13:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.00,0:13:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Brough Superier！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.00,0:13:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}注：Brough Superior SS100AGS\N被称为"机车中的劳斯莱斯"，全世界只有281台。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.40,0:13:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 为什么会在这种地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.87,0:13:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.43,0:13:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 好像是因为抛锚了所以一直放在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.31,0:13:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这辆车是你爷爷的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.39,0:13:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.50,0:13:56.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你修好它
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.90,0:14:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果修好的话 你可以把它骑走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.08,0:14:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在那之前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.64,0:14:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要载我游湖畔一周
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.73,0:14:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我和萤之助先生的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.30,0:14:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就为了这个 几十年都…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.12,0:14:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在这里等着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.19,0:14:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有你这句话…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.59,0:14:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 接下来…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.71,0:14:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这个是！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.08,0:14:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被称为“机车中的劳斯莱斯”的！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.66,0:14:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Brough Superior！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.10,0:14:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！这下我们机车社的财产就不愁了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.32,0:14:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宝物啊宝物 这下赚到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.51,0:14:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的难题是这些人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.08,0:14:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 这辆车请让我一个人来修理
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.55,0:14:58.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？森里 难道你想…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.24,0:15:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私吞吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.97,0:15:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.77,0:15:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你想一个人修呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.48,0:15:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为 这辆车必须由我亲手修好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.16,0:15:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.25,0:15:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运吗…那就没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.99,0:15:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田宮！大泷！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.28,0:15:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.56,0:15:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的哮喘旧病复发了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.86,0:15:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吧 小田
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.55,0:15:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扶我回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.09,0:15:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.30,0:15:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈…*你来的时候装在哪里的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.52,0:15:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森里 这个时代的机车基本上都是着重协调性的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.78,0:15:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛮特殊的 当心点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.48,0:15:49.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.32,0:15:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.39,0:15:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.06,0:15:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要赌气到什么时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.29,0:16:02.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 女神居然被思念体弄晕了 太没面子了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.41,0:16:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用那么在意啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.03,0:16:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是女神 但其实只是个小P孩嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.64,0:16:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 真讨厌！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.84,0:16:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兀儿德大笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.83,0:16:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.44,0:16:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.96,0:16:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了…有一点我没想明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.57,0:16:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎么知道她和萤一爷爷之间有某种联系的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.93,0:16:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为煮白薯的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.50,0:16:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煮白薯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.79,0:16:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她做的煮白薯的味道和小惠\N教我时煮出来的味道一模一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.96,0:16:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是所谓森里家的味道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.93,0:16:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有就是爷爷的照片和地图等的线索
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.11,0:16:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确是你的风格
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.13,0:17:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 这样好吗 萤一会被抢走哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.57,0:17:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很了解她的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.20,0:17:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终有一天我也会和萤一…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.93,0:17:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓儿丹蒂…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.82,0:17:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.22,0:17:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再跑一周！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.27,0:17:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那两个人居然乖乖地…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.28,0:17:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.29,0:17:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛 别管我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.47,0:17:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.16,0:17:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 这里电视的台很少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.99,0:17:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你妨碍我打扫了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.25,0:17:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天衣服干得真快呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.89,0:17:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.70,0:17:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.72,0:17:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么女神要作俯卧撑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.35,0:17:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.78,0:17:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这时放入鲜奶油
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.45,0:17:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.14,0:17:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样子比较高效率
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.09,0:17:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它说这里疼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.16,0:17:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.31,0:18:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 完成
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.37,0:18:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样明天就能跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.03,0:18:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.59,0:18:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…有件事想问你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.86,0:18:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.49,0:18:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得萤之助其实是想回到这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.56,0:18:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是最终却没有回来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.25,0:18:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这样而让你等了几十年
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.48,0:18:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有后悔过 如果没有遇到他就好了么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.85,0:18:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生病的时候 也曾经怨过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.62,0:18:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不来见我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.43,0:18:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管如此 与萤之助先生的相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.71,0:18:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍是我一生中最亮的光辉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.22,0:18:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…一定…比起没有相识而只是擦身而过…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.45,0:19:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是像这样痛苦的相遇 要好得多了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.25,0:19:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这究竟是对是错 明天应该就能知道答案了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.46,0:19:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.06,0:19:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.31,0:19:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.07,0:19:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.74,0:19:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.43,0:19:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.80,0:19:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拂面而过的轻风
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.28,0:19:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心旷神怡的鼓动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.37,0:19:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞬息而变的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.63,0:20:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.57,0:20:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想让畏惧病魔的我看的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.19,0:20:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,树木
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.58,0:20:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大地
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.07,0:20:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.91,0:20:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.39,0:20:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.30,0:20:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有这一切的命运 都将是消逝于这风中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.02,0:20:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…正因如此 与你的的相遇才更快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.40,0:20:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有在这…瞬间即逝的风中才能感受到…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.89,0:20:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤之助先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.01,0:20:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.46,0:20:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答应我任性的请求
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.32,0:20:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.40,0:21:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“再见”
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.03,0:21:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后 好像听到她这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.50,0:21:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的宝贝儿啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.77,0:21:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的要留下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.72,0:21:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 这是我和她的重叠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.73,0:21:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天可能我也会这样等待蓓儿丹蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.38,0:21:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.82,0:21:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以至少…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.75,0:21:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少把这辆机车 为了她…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.71,0:21:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会让萤一等几十年的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.03,0:21:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就好 我还在想 万一真要那样该怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.31,0:21:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会怎么样呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.32,0:21:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一边修机车一边等待
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.84,0:22:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 再见之时 载着你飞驰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.52,0:22:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在与你 与这么多人相遇的这个猫实镇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.54,0:22:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一…我能来到这里真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.35,0:22:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是 高原的旅社里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.77,0:22:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今仍有着一台Brough Superior
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.69,0:22:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此长眠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.57,0:23:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 不论何时都想向你传递
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.34,0:24:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那旋律载着无限的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.73,0:24:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.47,0:24:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回 啊啊 喜欢是动摇人心之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.55,0:24:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.38,0:24:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜…喜喜…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.21,0:24:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 干脆点吧！
